This directory contains tools required for development, maintenance and
release management of Einarc. It's generally not interesting for regular
users, so it should be excluded from distribution tarball.

== Memo: how to make a release

* Pump version in:
	VERSION
	lib/einarc.rb
* Document changes in NEWS
* Commit everything
* Set git tag for a release: "git tag vA.B.C"
* Push everything to github, including tags: "git push --tags"
* release-tarball
* Upload to SF
* Announce at:
	inquisitor.ru => Atom feed
	SourceForge.net (news submit)
	freecode.com
	linux.org.ru
	opennet.ru
	linux-raid mailing list
